de.iftm.dcm4che.router.plugin
Class PseudonymPlugin

java.lang.Object
  de.iftm.dcm4che.router.plugin.DicomRouterPlugin
      de.iftm.dcm4che.router.plugin.PseudonymPlugin

public class PseudonymPlugin
extends DicomRouterPlugin

This plugin replaces the PatientName with a pseudonym. The plugin supports the properties which start with the key PseudonymPlugin and have the subkeys:

type
The key may have one of the following predefined values:
#Initials2_Birdat4
Creates a new Patientname: ii_bbbbbb with
i the initials of the patient: name surename
b patient birth date

#Mod2Acqdat8_Birdat8
Creates a new Patientname: mmaaaaaaaa_bbbbbbbb with
m modality
a acquisition date
b patient birth date

Default value: #Initials2_Birdat4
